MBOMBELA – According to Sembcorp Silulumanzi spokesman Richmond Jele, the  following areas affected are KaNyamazane, Tekwane, Pienaar and surrounding areas up to Kabokweni. “It may take four to six hours to fix the problem. The result is that the water distribution schedule will be disrupted. Therefore please use your available water sparingly.” He concluded that Sembcorp Silulumanzi apologised for the  inconvenience caused.